{
  "message": "fix: Add test fixture data files to git\n\nThe .lance data files in tests/fixtures/*/data/ were incorrectly\nignored by the `data/` rule in .gitignore. This caused Zig tests\nto fail on CI because @embedFile paths couldn't be resolved.\n\nChanges:\n- Change `data/` to `/data/` in .gitignore (only ignore root /data/)\n- Add `!tests/fixtures/**/data/` to explicitly allow fixture data\n- Add all fixture data files needed by test_sql_executor.zig",
  "files": [
    {
      "sha": "738494d8e8dbf432272bcf2aff6259d7f8ff2e2e",
      "filename": ".gitignore",
      "status": "modified",
      "additions": 4,
      "deletions": 1,
      "changes": 5,
      "blob_url": "https://github.com/teamchong/lanceql/blob/f9e12d6bc7fa8509509f0afa9c4cbb89a6917580/.gitignore",
      "raw_url": "https://github.com/teamchong/lanceql/raw/f9e12d6bc7fa8509509f0afa9c4cbb89a6917580/.gitignore",
      "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/teamchong/lanceql/contents/.gitignore?ref=f9e12d6bc7fa8509509f0afa9c4cbb89a6917580",
      "patch": "@@ -33,7 +33,10 @@ Thumbs.db\n benchmarks/*.lance/\n benchmarks/*.parquet\n benchmarks/*_results.json\n-data/\n+/data/\n+\n+# Allow test fixture data\n+!tests/fixtures/**/data/\n *.dylib\n *.wasm\n !zig-out/bin/*.wasm"
